            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20prayer%20of%20the%20psalmist%20for%20God%20to%20come%20and%20change%20the%20world%20was%20a%20bold%20one.%20The%20closing%20hours%20of%20Jesus'%20life%20epitomized%20the%20answer%20to%20David's%20prayers.%20Jesus'%20slow%20and%20agonizing%20death%20on%20the%20cross%20caused%20the%20earth%20to%20convulse%20and%20quake.%20Even%20the%20sun%20refused%20to%20shine.%20The%20presence%20of%20the%20Lord%20was%20so%20awesome%20that%20the%20elements%20He%20had%20created%20were%20unable%20to%20function%20normally.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EEven%20the%20guards%20shook%20when%20the%20Lord%20of%20Life%20came%20out%20of%20the%20tomb%20(Matthew%2028%3A4).%20Mighty%20angels%20confronted%20the%20women%20who%20had%20come%20to%20anoint%20Jesus'%20body%2C%20and%20Luke%2024%3A5%20says%2C%20%22The%20women%20were%20terrified%20and%20bowed%20low%20before%20them.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWho%20can%20stand%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20almighty%20God%3F%20His%20presence%20will%20shake%20anything%20and%20everything%20until%20all%20creation%20acknowledges%20that%20%22the%20Lord%20reigns%22%20(Psalm%2099%3A1%20NIV).%20When%20God%20came%20down%20on%20Mount%20Sinai%2C%20the%20earth%20and%20mountain%20began%20to%20quake%20and%20shake%20violently%2C%20and%20the%20mountain%20was%20engulfed%20in%20fire%20and%20smoke%20(Exodus%2019%3A18).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod's%20kingdom%20is%20the%20only%20kingdom%20that%20cannot%20be%20shaken%20or%20destroyed%20(Hebrews%2012%3A28).%20Let%20the%20nations%20tremble%20under%20the%20Lordship%20of%20Christ.%20If%20the%20earth%20now%20shakes%20in%20His%20absence%2C%20what%20will%20it%20do%20when%20He%20personally%20appears%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
