            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Judges.8:18-9:21",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJudges%208%3A18-9%3A21%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_18%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Gideon%20asked%20Zebah%20and%20Zalmunna%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThe%20men%20you%20killed%20at%20Tabor%26%23x2014%3Bwhat%20were%20they%20like%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BLike%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BThey%20all%20had%20the%20look%20of%20a%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20son.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_19%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThey%20were%20my%20brothers%2C%20the%20sons%20of%20my%20own%20mother!%26%23x201D%3B%20Gideon%20exclaimed.%20%26%23x201C%3BAs%20surely%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20lives%2C%20I%20wouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20kill%20you%20if%20you%20hadn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20killed%20them.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_20%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3ETurning%20to%20Jether%2C%20his%20oldest%20son%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BKill%20them!%26%23x201D%3B%20But%20Jether%20did%20not%20draw%20his%20sword%2C%20for%20he%20was%20only%20a%20boy%20and%20was%20afraid.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_21%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Zebah%20and%20Zalmunna%20said%20to%20Gideon%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BBe%20a%20man!%20Kill%20us%20yourself!%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20Gideon%20killed%20them%20both%20and%20took%20the%20royal%20ornaments%20from%20the%20necks%20of%20their%20camels.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_22%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EGideon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Sacred%20Ephod%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Israelites%20said%20to%20Gideon%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BBe%20our%20ruler!%20You%20and%20your%20son%20and%20your%20grandson%20will%20be%20our%20rulers%2C%20for%20you%20have%20rescued%20us%20from%20Midian.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_23%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Gideon%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20not%20rule%20over%20you%2C%20nor%20will%20my%20son.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20rule%20over%20you!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_24%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20do%20have%20one%20request%26%23x2014%3Bthat%20each%20of%20you%20give%20me%20an%20earring%20from%20the%20plunder%20you%20collected%20from%20your%20fallen%20enemies.%26%23x201D%3B%20(The%20enemies%2C%20being%20Ishmaelites%2C%20all%20wore%20gold%20earrings.)%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_25%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGladly!%26%23x201D%3B%20they%20replied.%20They%20spread%20out%20a%20cloak%2C%20and%20each%20one%20threw%20in%20a%20gold%20earring%20he%20had%20gathered%20from%20the%20plunder.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_26%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20weight%20of%20the%20gold%20earrings%20was%20forty-three%20pounds%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A26%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E1%2C700%20%5Bshekels%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B19.4%26%23xA0%3Bkilograms%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20not%20including%20the%20royal%20ornaments%20and%20pendants%2C%20the%20purple%20clothing%20worn%20by%20the%20kings%20of%20Midian%2C%20or%20the%20chains%20around%20the%20necks%20of%20their%20camels.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_27%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EGideon%20made%20a%20sacred%20ephod%20from%20the%20gold%20and%20put%20it%20in%20Ophrah%2C%20his%20hometown.%20But%20soon%20all%20the%20Israelites%20prostituted%20themselves%20by%20worshiping%20it%2C%20and%20it%20became%20a%20trap%20for%20Gideon%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_28%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EThat%20is%20the%20story%20of%20how%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20defeated%20Midian%2C%20which%20never%20recovered.%20Throughout%20the%20rest%20of%20Gideon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20lifetime%26%23x2014%3Babout%20forty%20years%26%23x2014%3Bthere%20was%20peace%20in%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_29%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Gideon%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A29%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJerub-baal%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20see%206%3A32.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20son%20of%20Joash%20returned%20home.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_30%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20had%20seventy%20sons%20born%20to%20him%2C%20for%20he%20had%20many%20wives.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_31%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20also%20had%20a%20concubine%20in%20Shechem%2C%20who%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20son%2C%20whom%20he%20named%20Abimelech.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_32%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EGideon%20died%20when%20he%20was%20very%20old%2C%20and%20he%20was%20buried%20in%20the%20grave%20of%20his%20father%2C%20Joash%2C%20at%20Ophrah%20in%20the%20land%20of%20the%20clan%20of%20Abiezer.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_33%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Gideon%20died%2C%20the%20Israelites%20prostituted%20themselves%20by%20worshiping%20the%20images%20of%20Baal%2C%20making%20Baal-berith%20their%20god.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_34%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20forgot%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20their%20God%2C%20who%20had%20rescued%20them%20from%20all%20their%20enemies%20surrounding%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_8_35%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3ENor%20did%20they%20show%20any%20loyalty%20to%20the%20family%20of%20Jerub-baal%20(that%20is%2C%20Gideon)%2C%20despite%20all%20the%20good%20he%20had%20done%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJudges%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAbimelech%20Rules%20over%20Shechem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOne%20day%20Gideon%26%23x2019%3Bs%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJerub-baal%26%23x2019%3Bs%3C%2Fem%3E%20(see%206%3A32)%3B%20also%20in%209%3A2%2C%2024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20son%20Abimelech%20went%20to%20Shechem%20to%20visit%20his%20uncles%26%23x2014%3Bhis%20mother%26%23x2019%3Bs%20brothers.%20He%20said%20to%20them%20and%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20mother%26%23x2019%3Bs%20family%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAsk%20the%20leading%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20be%20ruled%20by%20all%20seventy%20of%20Gideon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sons%20or%20by%20one%20man.%20And%20remember%20that%20I%20am%20your%20own%20flesh%20and%20blood!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Abimelech%26%23x2019%3Bs%20uncles%20gave%20his%20message%20to%20all%20the%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20on%20his%20behalf.%20And%20after%20listening%20to%20this%20proposal%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Shechem%20decided%20in%20favor%20of%20Abimelech%20because%20he%20was%20their%20relative.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20gave%20him%20seventy%20silver%20coins%20from%20the%20temple%20of%20Baal-berith%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20hire%20some%20reckless%20troublemakers%20who%20agreed%20to%20follow%20him.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20went%20to%20his%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20home%20at%20Ophrah%2C%20and%20there%2C%20on%20one%20stone%2C%20they%20killed%20all%20seventy%20of%20his%20half%20brothers%2C%20the%20sons%20of%20Gideon.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EJerub-baal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(see%206%3A32)%3B%20also%20in%209%3A16%2C%2019%2C%2028%2C%2057.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20But%20the%20youngest%20brother%2C%20Jotham%2C%20escaped%20and%20hid.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20all%20the%20leading%20citizens%20of%20Shechem%20and%20Beth-millo%20called%20a%20meeting%20under%20the%20oak%20beside%20the%20pillar%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20at%20Shechem%20and%20made%20Abimelech%20their%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJotham%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Parable%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20Jotham%20heard%20about%20this%2C%20he%20climbed%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Mount%20Gerizim%20and%20shouted%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BListen%20to%20me%2C%20citizens%20of%20Shechem!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EListen%20to%20me%20if%20you%20want%20God%20to%20listen%20to%20you!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22judg_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22judg%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%